data.description: Located in the highly sought out Minquadale neighborhood, this delightful cape cod is just a short drive away from a variety of shopping facilities and the Wilmington Riverwalk. This home is perfectly situated near major thoroughfares and less than a 10-minute drive to the Wilmington Amtrak station, making it an optimal choice for commuters. Features include first floor laundry, central air, a very spacious lot, wood flooring in living and dining rooms, and new carpet in bedrooms. With its combination of layout, functionality, and location, this home is truly a gem with lots of potential. Home is being sold in As-Is condition and is ready to show!!
